text: Fabian Malleier (born 4 January 1998) is an Italian luger. He competed in the men's doubles event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. Malleier is an athlete of the Gruppo Sportivo Esercito. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male lugers Category:Olympic lugers of Italy Category:Lugers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Competitors at the 2016 Winter Youth Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Sportspeople from Merano Category:Lugers of Gruppo Sportivo Esercito
